cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper discusses supervised hashing for document classification and retrieval, as well as image-related tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses evaluation protocols and baselines, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
